      "Both sub-scenarios share the same initial setup.",
      "The designer's notes describe both scenarios as 'stultifying' and 'dull'; included for historical completeness.",
      "ALL Axis infantry-type units are reduced to 2/3 (fractions rounded up) of their maximum TOE Strength at setup.",
      "Extensive minefield and fortification setup — most complex construction state of any scenario.",
      "El Alamein front: Commonwealth in map E, Axis front along D-E border.",
      "Air forces stubbed — land game only for MVP.",
      "OCR artifacts: 'nd New Zeland' → '2nd New Zealand'; hex codes with leading 'I' likely 'D' or 'E' (corrected where obvious)."
    ]
  },

